    "title": "Senior Talent Engagement Analyst",
    "excerpt": "<p>We are hiring a Senior Talent Engagement Analyst (Analyst III) to join the Talent team! In this role you will&nbsp; play a key role in ODI’s talent acquisition, classification and compensation analysis, workforce planning, employee engagement, and workforce compliance activities.&nbsp; Location: ODI staff reside throughout California. The employee’s workstation is located in Sacramento, CA. Travel &#8230; <a title=\"Senior Talent Engagement Analyst\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/join-us/senior-talent-engagement-analyst/\" aria-label=\"More on Senior Talent Engagement Analyst\">Read more</a></p>\n",
